hopobject.body: I'll send you a text vazomyne pastillas 2. NICK FOLES BOUNCES BACK WELL FROM MISTAKES: Last week, Foles led the Eagles to a TD drive after fumbling on his first series. He started 6 for 6 this week before throwing an interception in the end zone after dropping a shot-gun snap and trying to get rid of the ball. But Foles came back and led the Eagles to a TD on his next drive, running it in himself from the 7. Foles was 6 of 8 for 53 yards. He's 11 of 14 for 96 yards, no TDs, one pick and a passer rating of 65.7 in two games.
